('7017e188-4586-4f79-adfd-a9409c358b34','What is CosmicEdge?','what-is-cosmicedge','CosmicEdge is a hybrid sports intelligence platform combining statistical modeling, simulation, and celestial overlays to surface edges in player props and game outcomes.','CosmicEdge is a hybrid sports intelligence platform that blends traditional sports analytics with celestial pattern recognition. The platform combines statistical projections, trend analysis, simulation modeling, behavioral streak detection, and astrological timing overlays into a unified probability framework designed to identify prop edges and betting inefficiencies.','info','all',1,true,'[]','[]','2026-03-11 15:23:47.578767+00','2026-03-11 15:23:47.578767+00'),
